# Container CVEs may only be suppressed when all of these are true:
# - the component is vendored by an upstream runtime and cannot be upgraded here;
# - a fresh no-cache image scan proves the finding remains after upstream refresh;
# - the entry links a tracking issue and expires within 30 days.
# Actionable first-party or directly upgradeable findings remain blocking.
